                            <div class="testimonials_item text-center">
                                <div class="quote">“</div>
                                <p class="testimonials_text">Truly grateful to the generations of teachers who are teaching day and night to provide society with engineers: Good competence - Hard work - Passion for creativity, these are the most important qualities of those who want create and change the world.</p>
                                <div class="testimonial_user">
                                    <div class="testimonial_image mx-auto">
                                        <img src="~/Content/Client/images/Student/student_Duy3.jpg" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="testimonial_name">Ho Ngoc Tu Duy</div>
                                    <div class="testimonial_title">Graduate Student</div>
